  <description><![CDATA[<p>All aspects of the brand new Hotel St. Alban have been well thought out from the beautiful combination of wood and stone for elegance, to the soft lighting of the bar for a feeling of intimacy and the 250m² spa for relaxation. Breakfast will be provided at the hotel and the optional 3 course dinner can be taken at the <em>La Scierie</em> (10 minutes’ walk) - a beautifully restored Savoyard restaurant.</p>
<p>Situated in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/597c2d8b93354bef8c187c100894c3f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/597c2d8b93354bef8c187c100894c3f9}" title="La Clusaz">La Clusaz</a>, the hotel also offers a complimentary shuttle to the slopes.</p>]]></description>
