  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All rooms have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking), bath with shower head attachment, cable / satellite flat screen TV with English speaking channels and on demand services, bed linen, towels, slippers, toiletries, safe, telephone, bath robes, hairdryer, coffee machine, electric kettle, mini bar and a balcony with mountain views.</p>
<ul>
<li>Classic room (A2): sleeps 2 people (18m²). Also available for sole occupancy, on request (F1)</li>
<li>Superior room (B3): sleeps 2 adults and one child (under 12 years) on a single sofa bed (25m²)</li>
</ul>
<p>Interconnecting rooms are available (on request). Wake up services are available from reception. Superior (B3) rooms are suitable for a baby cot.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
